        public void CANCEL_UPLOAD_FILES_TC()
        Summary
        Cancel upload files
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        Steps
        1. Click on Upload document button
        2. Select files from TestData location
        3. Click on close button('X' button) on window
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify Files should not be uploaded

      • UPLOAD_FILES_WITH_SAME_NAME_TC

        public void UPLOAD_FILES_WITH_SAME_NAME_TC()
        Summary
        Upload files with same name
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        Steps
        1. Click on Upload document button
        2. Select files from TestData location

        4. Click on Start Upload button
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify Files should be uploaded and synchronized successfully and visible on DashBoard

      • DO_NOT_UPLOAD_FILES_WITH_SAME_NAME_TC

        public void DO_NOT_UPLOAD_FILES_WITH_SAME_NAME_TC()
        Summary
        Do not Upload files with same name
        Pre-Conditions
        DashBoard page should be open
        Steps
        1. Click on Upload document button
        2. Select files from TestData location
        3. Click on 'No' button on window stating 'File already exists'
        4. Click on close('X') button if not files is available to upload. OR Click Start upload if files available to upload
        Expected Result:
        1. Verify Files having same name should not be uploaded and visible on DashBoard
